appear to contradict the text in places (and I seem to remember that some
of the text contradicts itself).  Another source of information is the
TNS printed in JTAS, which detail the 5FW.  One of the JTAS had
"Traveller News Service Revisited" which recaps the news of the 5FW.
This also contradicts the text in The Spinward Marches Campaign (Imperial
propaganda?)  I think the 5FW game includes TNS items leading up to the
war; any chance I could get those from someone?

