    'from' => 'caw@intercon.com',
    'body' => 'Eris Reddoch said:
> Marc Miller has written that Traveller rights devolve to him. I don\'t
> know why Mr Miller walked away from GDW and Traveller a few years
> ago.  I\'ve heard it was because he was \'burned out\' on trying to make
