(Like the fact that there is actually a chance of missing your target with
a TL 15 weapon). This may be serious flaws as far as you are concerned, but
I\'m resigned to them. Because it\'s my belief that the future, if
_realistically_ portrayed is a fine place to live, but a damn dull place to
adventure in (Well, propably there\'ll be all sorts of neat things to do, but
