    'body' => 'I forgot a couple of further points about why there should be such a range
of TL across the Imperium and why TL hasn\'t progressed further than TL15/16...

To draw a quick analogy with the modern world, low TL populations are a
cheap work force to produce goods for higher TL populations.

There you have it. 50% of the reason for the varied TLs. The higher TL
people don\'t have any great incentive to bring their poorer neighbours up to
their own TL because then who would they get to produce all their luxury
home wares at such low prices?

The other 50%? Well, give people TL and they become dangerous. Particularly
anyone with high TL weapons. Just think of the destructive power of
explosives and nukes today. Do you want to provide your enemies (or even
anyone you\'re not quite sure about) with the TL to handle say radioactives
easily, or fusion power... Technology is POWER. No one gives power away
willy-nilly. Scale this up to Imperium level. Ever notice how the major
research installations marked throughout the Imperium are all... Imperial...
you can bet your bottom dollar the Imperium has a certain amount of limited
resources which have developed to TL16, 17 or higher. But if they let it
become common knowledge, then everyone will want some. e.g. today: got a
miraculous cure for cancer, but it costs a few million? Watch the
millionaires queue up, but is any government going to pay for its common
citizens to be cured at that cost? Worse, if it\'s military tech we\'re
talking about, thing of the worries if it falls into the hands of the enemy!
Then think about cartels. Look at what would happen today if someone came
along, "Man in the White Suit" style and said I\'ve created untearable,
unstainable fabric. No one need buy new clothes - these will last you your
entire life. You can bet they\'d be found floating in a river, dead from
multiple scissor wounds... yet another way of stifling new technology.

Basically, anything above TL15 in the Imperium is Imperium-run and quite
secret. And a wide range of lower TL planets are encouraged to provide cheap
labour and goods for the higher TL worlds.

Anyone care to work out similar or alternative strategies for the other
races: Zhodani, etc.?

Andy Lilly
Coordinating BITS (British Isles Traveller Support)

