    'index' => 'ac515',
    'month' => '02',
    'body' => '>I am sorry David but you missed my point. I have never denied that j-torps
>provide a faster passage of information. The point I was merely trying to
>make was that introduction of j-torps doesn\'t necessarily mean the
>marginalisation of the X-Boat Service. I gave the example of Railways and
