urgency was sent by train.

The situation with jump torps is even worse because, not only
are they faster, but they are available for use directly on
worlds off an X-boat route.  (ie you telegraph isn\'t just strung
along the rail lines, but goes to every town.)

>I suggest you read responses to your posts carefully in future.

