Some people have higher standards.  At least with J-drive it is part
of the fundamental suspension of disbelief (see my earlier comments
on this subject) and the background was written with knowledge and
thought of the consequences of the technology.  This is always better
than adding technologies to a background that is already set without
regard for the consequences.


