Not in the 1st edition rules.  The 1st edition had you roll 3D and
subtract 8.  This lead to a very unrealistic situation where you
could pump somebody full of bullets from your pistol, and wind up
doing no damage...since the average die roll would be 9-8=1.  Quite
often you wound up doing negative damage...

