Probably a wise decision.

>However, I would be interested to hear how the argument boils down to,
>like the Great Feudal Technocracy Debate ("You can define it anyway you
>choose") and the Fabulous Jump Rock-Throwing Contest ("You can\'t stop
>jump rocks at velocity").

I\'m not sure what you want.  The main disagreement, for me at least,
is...Is the presence of ability to send messages through jump
space, in small portable "torpedoes", consistent with the Traveller
background as written?  I would say the answer is no.  That
