>MT material.  I\'ve run into at least three references to a human minor
>race known as the Suerrat (Solomani & Aslan, MTJ #3, and the old CT
>Library data, book A-M).  They seem to be hairy, short, and come from
>Ilelish 2907.  Does anyone know of any more info published on them.  Data
