In answer to Philip McGregor\'s message about the too tiny size of the =
Terran population compared to the Vilani:

There\'s an easy answer to the question of how Terra\'s population quickly =
exploded in just 300 years: Cloning. Make as many clones as you want of =
lots of different people and place them on the new worlds - instant =
colony!

I\'m not saying this is how it happened/happens :-), but only that this =
is a logical solution.

