that *all* of the adult inhabitants are skilled and pulling their weight ...
can you afford to give non-feminist traditionally oriented women the space when
you could have a family that has two skills for the price of one? Who is more
likely to be able to afford the fare, if such is the way of getting offplanet?
A family with one breadwinner or one with two?

Nope, your explanation doesn\'t seem (to me, anyway) to work in this instance.

Phil


